casebody.data:
Brian WILLIAMS, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
MCKENZIE CAPITAL LLC, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D16-1394 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. NOVEMBER 30, 2017 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and LAGOA and FERNANDEZ, JJ., concur.

Upon the Court's own motion, it is ordered that the above styled appeal is hereby dismissed as taken from a non-final, non-appealable order and note that because the trial court set aside the default, the appeal is moot.
